description:
Just over a year ago, the Russo-Ukrainian conflict began in Ukraine.

This week, ANN talks with Hope Channel Ukraine about evangelistic growth despite the ongoing challenges the country is facing. ANN Video also looks at ADRA's humanitarian relief work in Brazil and its new office in Cape Verde.

Watch these stories and others from around the world.

For more Adventist news, subscribe to our Youtube channel.

ANN is the official news channel of the Seventh-day Adventist Church. For all things Adventist news, visit adventist.news
